<section class="section section-light">
<h2>Early life</h2>
<p>Virat Kohli was born on 5 November 1988 in Delhi to a Punjabi Khatri Hindu family.[8] His father, Prem Kohli, worked as a criminal lawyer and his mother, Saroj Kohli, is a housewife.[9] He has an older brother, Vikas, and an older sister, Bhawna.[10] According to his family, when he was three-years old, Kohli would pick up a cricket bat, start swinging it and ask his father to bowl at him.[11]</p>
</section>
