    <h2>Personal Life</h2>
    <p>Kohli started dating Bollywood actress Anushka Sharma in 2013; the couple soon earned the portmanteau "Virushka".[396][397] Their relationship attracted substantial media attention, with persistent rumours and speculations in the media, as neither of the two publicly talked about it.[398] The couple married on 11 December 2017 in a private ceremony in Florence, Italy.[399] On 11 January 2021, their first child, a girl, was born.[400]Kohli started dating Bollywood actress Anushka Sharma in 2013; the couple soon earned the portmanteau "Virushka".[396][397] Their relationship attracted substantial media attention, with persistent rumours and speculations in the media, as neither of the two publicly talked about it.[398] The couple married on 11 December 2017 in a private ceremony in Florence, Italy.[399] On 11 January 2021, their first child, a girl, was born.[400]</p>
